  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Serum phosphorus measurement ≥4.6 mg/dL (≥1.49 mmol/L) and ≤5.5 mg/dL (≤1.76 mmol/L
             after discontinuation of current phosphate binder therapy if applicable.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Active dysphagia or swallowing disorder or a predisposition to or current bowel
             obstruction, ileus, or severe gastrointestinal motility disorders including severe
             constipation.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
